title: Tech View: Nifty50 sees selling at 20-EMA; stay neutral, say analysts - Economic Times
content: Tech View: Nifty50 sees selling at 20-EMA; stay neutral, say analysts  Economic Times
description: Amol Athawale of Kotak Securities said Nifty has traded above the 50-day SMA, but is seeing profit booking near the 20-day SMA or 17,800 level.
